data.description: Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this centrally located Biloxi home yours. Experience the best of coastal living with nearby military facilities, pristine beaches, convenient shopping, boating, and golf. Schedule a showing today and make this your new home sweet home! New LVP flooring and paint. First Right of Refusal is in place but don't let that stop you from touring this home!
